headline: American Water Works (AWK) Soars 3.8%: Is Further Upside Left in the Stock?
summary: American Water Works (AWK) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
